Package: ClusVis
Type: Package
Title: Gaussian-Based Visualization of Generic Model-Based Clustering
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Biernacki, C. and Marbac, M. and Vandewalle, V.
Maintainer: Marbac, M. <matthieu.marbac@gmail.com>
